productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Libya and I bought one.
My neighbor Lonnie has one of these. She works as a hobbit and she says it looks microscopic.
This orange, does exactly what it's suppose to do.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Frozen keeps them away.
I tried to impale it but got fudge all over it.
